  "sourceFacts": [
    "The Fatory Team Members source card keeps the social links inside a white horizontal bar that overlaps the lower part of each image card.",
    "The social bar is not a loose icon row below the card and does not replace Font Awesome social icons with generated art.",
    "The repeated Fatory section heading pattern uses `.site-heading h2` with Inter, 52px desktop font size, 600 weight, 62.4px line-height, 1px letter spacing, 20px bottom padding, and red divider pseudo-elements under the H2: a 40px line plus a short 5px segment.",
    "The red divider is a source-wide section-title system for repeated centered section headings including Work Process, Portfolio, Team Members, and Blog; it is not a Team-only exception.",
    "The Fatory Team Members hover does not snap to a fast full-card blackout; member info fades with slower ease-in-out timing while the overlay text slides upward over the darkened image.",
    "The Fatory testimonials section places the faint quote ornament on the left/title-side wrapper pseudo-element `.testimonial-items::after`; it is not rendered behind the right testimonial text.",
    "The Fatory testimonial carousel nav icons use source-compatible Font Awesome angle markup: `fa fa-angle-left` and `fa fa-angle-right`.",
    "The Fatory testimonial carousel is finite (`loop: false`) and Owl's disabled nav control is visibly dimmed at the boundary; the first slide must show the previous control as disabled instead of two equally active black arrows."
  ],
